{"tid":963920,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"不如大家一人寄一包飲筒比綠色和平","createTime":"2019-01-01T00:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T03:07:25.000Z","uid":127611,"like":107,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"380fba71799ee6c907411c2113ffb586b4d5475f","tid":963920,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"而家周圍都冇哂飲筒<br />\n綠色和平啲人食M記個陣一定好唔方便<br />\n又搞到牙齒敏感<br />\n咁就不如大家一人去超市買包飲筒<br />\n再寄去比綠色和平啲人用<br />\n一包飲筒先十零蚊，唔貴<br />\n但咁就可以幫到人，自己又開心<br />\n你地話係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.greenpeace.org/hk/high/About-Us/Contact-Us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.greenpeace.org%2Fhk%2Fhigh%2FAbout-Us%2FContact-Us%2F&d=1lm22OwW0kEzPW3%2FCgxlkG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d9a329ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.greenpeace.org/hk/high/About-Us/Contact-Us/</a>"},{"pid":"afdc08f4fffd04597e6f8042df8f657fb6e2e651","tid":963920,"uid":191815,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"寄畀佢咪盞益咗佢<br />\n計我話就一人買一包，去到啲走飲筒嘅餐廳，當住啲環保撚面前即用即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6356faf958307e4c5cf9638fa190795c72f3ed","tid":963920,"uid":142279,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"寄畀佢哋用？緊係枝枝都咬爛個頭，之後包埋寄過去，等佢哋拎去掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e892f6efbc5befec286c7f184b8c156ba2ad1e","tid":963920,"uid":127611,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"afdc08f4fffd04597e6f8042df8f657fb6e2e651","tid":963920,"uid":191815,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"寄畀佢咪盞益咗佢<br />\n計我話就一人買一包，去到啲走飲筒嘅餐廳，當住啲環保撚面前即用即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"我地既原意就係益人同幫人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只想大家踴躍參與，佢地就可以成個office都係飲管<br />\n黎緊10年都唔怕冇得用<br />\n有財力既巴打以捐多幾包<br />\n或者參加月捐計晝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c913321bb98b2f4dfebd16b76bf15ebfab61951","tid":963920,"uid":33391,"like":13,"dislike":73,"score":-60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"兒登真係兒登<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理性啲用下個腦諗野好唔好呀小朋友？"},{"pid":"7088dddf0748ee8f3fefa5de0300c49751a4d168","tid":963920,"uid":8048,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"經環保撚開光拎去義賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc9246429a8c3e623707ec3a16886239238aa73","tid":963920,"uid":127611,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7088dddf0748ee8f3fefa5de0300c49751a4d168","tid":963920,"uid":8048,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"經環保撚開光拎去義賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"咁就好<br />\n同綠色和平一齊推廣飲管文化<br />\n再等班環保人士買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70124c2888fbc67d7fbb7a3a336f007132c05cb","tid":963920,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"對付環保撚：迫佢扔垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d73e78ef90a235dd3423cae7dbd2955834d58bd","tid":963920,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c70124c2888fbc67d7fbb7a3a336f007132c05cb","tid":963920,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:47:38.000Z","msg":"對付環保撚：迫佢扔垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"唔係垃圾黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每支飲管都包含住我地既愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkg